## Ubuntu Build Environment

if use root user, set environment FORCE_UNSAFE_CONFIGURE=1
```
# 22.04
sudo apt install build-essential clang flex bison g++ gawk \
gcc-multilib g++-multilib gettext git libncurses-dev libssl-dev \
python3-distutils python3-setuptools rsync swig unzip zlib1g-dev file wget

# 24.04
sudo apt install build-essential clang flex bison g++ gawk \
gcc-multilib g++-multilib gettext git libncurses5-dev libssl-dev \
python3-setuptools rsync swig unzip zlib1g-dev file wget
```

## Build OpenWrt source code

```
git clone -b v24.10.0 --single-branch  https://git.openwrt.org/openwrt/openwrt.git
./scripts/feeds update -a
./scripts/feeds install -a

# generate .config file
make menuconfig

make download
make -j20

--> output
bin/targets/x86/generic/
config.buildinfo
feeds.buildinfo
openwrt-x86-generic-generic-ext4-combined-efi.img.gz
```

## Config Example

```
LuCI
  ├─ Collections  
  │   ├─ luci                                         # 核心包
  │   └─ luci-ssl                                     # SSL支持             
  └─ Modules
      ├─ Translations
      │   └─ Chinese Simplified (zh_Hans) (NEW)       # 中文语言包
      └─ luci-comppat                                 # 兼容性包  

Administration
  └─ btop                                   # 系统监控
Network
  ├─ File Transfer
  │   ├─ curl
  │   └─ wget
  ├─ SSH
      └─ openssh-sftp-server                # SSH服务
Utilities
  ├─ Compression
  │   ├─ gzip
  │   └─ unzip
  ├─ Disc
  │   ├─ blkid                              # 磁盘信息
  │   ├─ fdisk                              # 分区管理
  │   └─ lsblk                              # 磁盘信息
  ├─ Editors
  │   └─ vim
  ├─ Filesystems
  │   ├─ dosfstools
  │   ├─ e2fsprogs
  │   └─ exfat-mkfs
  └─ Shells
      └─ bash
```


*Reference*

https://openwrt.org/docs/guide-developer/toolchain/install-buildsystem

http://downloads.openwrt.org/releases/24.10.0/targets/x86/64/
